WEBVTT

00:00:06.404 --> 00:00:16.834 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
<b>I’m just a cart made up of bits and pieces—</b>
<b>A frame, a handle, and some wheels.</b>

00:00:16.834 --> 00:00:25.011 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
<b>But I’m a cart that helps to give a witness.</b>
<b>What is that like?</b>

00:00:25.011 --> 00:00:29.892 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
<b>Let me tell you how it feels.</b>

00:00:29.892 --> 00:00:41.699 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
<b>If you could see what I see</b><b>,</b>
<b>If you could visit all the places that I go</b><b>,</b>

00:00:41.699 --> 00:00:46.956 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
<b>If you could see the people there</b>

00:00:46.956 --> 00:00:52.881 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
<b>And get a glimpse of all the faces</b>
<b>that I get to know</b><b>,</b>

00:00:52.881 --> 00:00:58.304 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
<b>If you could hear what I hear</b>

00:00:58.304 --> 00:01:04.521 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
<b>When they see things </b>
<b>they’ve never had a chance to see</b><b>,</b>

00:01:04.521 --> 00:01:15.535 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
<b>That’s when you’ll see how it can be</b>
<b>That forever they’ll remember me.</b>

00:01:15.535 --> 00:01:21.292 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
<b>I’ve got wheels; I’ve got racks;</b>
<b>I’ve got books, and I’ve got tracts.</b>

00:01:21.292 --> 00:01:26.925 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
<b>I take the Kingdom message ev’</b><b>r</b><b>ywhere.</b>

00:01:26.925 --> 00:01:32.974 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
<b>When the crowds pass me by,</b>
<b>I’m designed to catch their eye.</b>

00:01:32.974 --> 00:01:40.109 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
<b>Wherever people gather, </b>
<b>count on me ’cause I’ll be there.</b>

00:01:40.109 --> 00:01:46.242 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
<b>If you could do what I do,</b>

00:01:46.242 --> 00:01:52.750 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
<b>You’d know the happiness </b>
<b>that always fills my heart.</b>

00:01:52.750 --> 00:02:12.943 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
<b>What a feeling to go wheeling!</b>
<b>I’m so glad to be a public</b><b>-</b><b>witness cart.</b>

